{{champion:77}} 
Considering Udyr's only real gate is mana, I expected him to be really strong.

His constant W allows him to tank the harass well, but because his damage is designed around the 2 second cooldown all of his abilities are less impactful than everyone else's with the same cooldowns. He isn't really able to 1v1 anyone, although maxing bear stance is fun.

{{champion:43}} 

I don't even want to play anyone else. She's so freaking strong.

Q is always up and the ultimate is only on cooldown for like 5 seconds and you get it at level 1.

